tafsir[6]{c,v,t}:
  15,38,"unto the day of a known time.'"
  15,40,"excepting those Thy servants among them that are devoted."
  15,43,"being perverse; Gehenna shall be their promised land all together."
  15,45,"But the godfearing shall be amidst gardens and fountains:"
  15,47,"We shall strip away all rancour that is in their breasts; as brothers they shall be upon couches set face to face;"
  15,50,"and that My chastisement is the painful chastisement."